      "date": "2013-11-05 01:54:05.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: (5 inline comments)\n\nIt isn't very clear from the description which patch re-fixes the problem of LU-2622?  It would be better to make that clear in the commit comment, since we don't want this patch to land, but the one that fixes the problem is delayed for some reason and the CPU usage that LU-2622 fixed is left in the next release.",
